#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2
msgid "Vector geometry"
msgstr "Vektorinė geometrija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:15
msgid "Add geometry attributes"
msgstr "Pridėti geometrijos atributus"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:16
msgid ""
"Computes geometric properties of the features in a vector layer and includes"
" them in the output layer."
msgstr ""
"Paskaičiuoja vektorinio sluoksnio geoobjektų geometrijos savybes ir įtraukia"
" jas į išvesties sluoksnį."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:19
msgid ""
"It generates a new vector layer with the same content as the input one, but "
"with additional attributes, containing geometric measurements based on a "
"selected CRS."
msgstr ""
"Sukuria naują sluoksnį su tokiu pačiu turiniu, kaip ir įvesties, bet su "
"papildomais atributais, kuriuose yra geometriniai matavimai paremti nurodyta"
" CRS."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:23
msgid ""
"The attributes added to the table depend on the geometry type and dimension "
"of the input layer:"
msgstr ""
"Į lentelę pridedami atributai priklauso nuo įvesties sluoksnio geometrijos "
"tipo ir matmenų:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:26
msgid ""
"for **point** layers: X (``xcoord``), Y (``ycoord``), Z (``zcoord``) "
"coordinates and/or M value (``mvalue``)"
msgstr ""
"**taškų** sluoksniams: X (``xcoord``), Y (``ycoord``), Z (``zcoord``) "
"koordinatės ir/ar M reikšmė (``mvalue``)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:28
msgid ""
"for **line** layers: ``length`` and, for the LineString and CompoundCurve "
"geometry types, the feature ``sinuosity`` and straight distance "
"(``straightdis``)"
msgstr ""
"**linijos** sluoksniams: ``length``, o LineString ir CompoundCurve "
"geometrijos tipams dar ir ``sinuosity`` bei tiesus atstumas "
"(``straightdis``)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:31
msgid "for **polygon** layers: ``perimeter`` and ``area``"
msgstr "**poligonų** sluoksniams: ``perimeter`` ir ``area``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:33
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:262
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3351
msgid ""
"This algorithm uses ellipsoid based measurements and respects the current "
":ref:`ellipsoid settings <measurements_ellipsoid>`."
msgstr ""
"Šis algoritmas naudoja elipse paremtus skaičiavimus ir atsižvelgia į "
"dabartinius :ref:`elipsoido nustatymus <measurements_ellipsoid>`."

